			<tr>
			<td>
				<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="3"><b>    Bard Particle Weapon</b>&nbsp;<a href="../Subscribe.asp?DID=228071"><font face="Verdana" size="2">[Subscribe to this document]</font></a></font>
					<br>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">
					<b><a href="mailto:">Kianye Sirenblades</a> | 
		                        9/27/2000 3:47:52 PM</b></font></p>
					
					<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">Does anyone know where to start the Fiery-Avenger Style Bard quest? I went to the Temple of Sol Ro to ask the guy that did the Lambent Greaves.<BR>
<BR>
When you first hail him, he tells you about lambent armor and then... to &quot;remember to ask me about a new bardic weapon&quot;.  aid everything I could think of to trigger a response regarding the weapon, but with no success.<BR>
<BR>
Kianye Sirenblades<BR>
41st Season Bardess of Prexus
			<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></p>
